{
  "texts": [
    "This step was performed to decrease the number of triangles within the STL file to accelerate the refinement process, but it may lead to cavities and poor representation of the original geometry in regions with high curvature.",
    "Therefore, cells in these regions, although invalid when compared to the original geometry, may be considered valid when using the coarsened geometry.",
    "(a) original grid in the x-z-plane (b) original grid in the y-z-plane Figure 10:10Figure 10: Original grid in the x-z-plane at x/MAC ≈ 4.9 (10a) and in the y-z-plane at y/MAC ≈ 0.9 (10b).",
    "The airfoil geometry is proprietary to Airbus and therefore redacted in fig.",
    "(a) grid generated by S 3 in the x-z-plane (b) grid generated by S 3 in the y-z-plane (c) interpolated metric field in the x-z-plane (d) interpolated metric field in the y-z-plane Figure 11:11Figure 11: Grid generated by S 3 in the x-z-plane at x/MAC ≈ 4.9 (11a) and the y-z-plane at y/MAC ≈ 0.9 (11b)."
  ]
}